</style><h3 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading">活跃于VTuber行业初期的老牌人才之一</h3><p></p><p>樋木美羽于 2018 年 10 月出道。 “<em>未来V-Singer。来自未来的交流，在这个时代做VTuber</em> 。”</p><p> 2021 年 1 月 16 日，Hizuki 发布了一段西班牙语视频。这在拉丁美洲的西班牙语国家引起了轰动，除了Hizuki在该地区的知名度不断提高外，他所属的WACTOR Co., Ltd.和WACTOR Productions也开始向该地区扩张。 . </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="5YK9kGO1CE"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/wactor-vtuber-hizuki-miu-espernol-signs-of-popularity-in-the-language-area-the-number-of-youtube-subscribers-has-skyrocketed-in-the-last-4-days/">WACTOR Hizuki Miu 西语国家走红迹象 最近4天频道订阅人数激增</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“WACTOR Hizuki Miu 在过去 4 天在西班牙语地区的频道订户迅速增加” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/wactor-vtuber-hizuki-miu-espernol-signs-of-popularity-in-the-language-area-the-number-of-youtube-subscribers-has-skyrocketed-in-the-last-4-days/embed/#?secret=TcQwNeDiyM#?secret=5YK9kGO1CE" data-secret="5YK9kGO1CE" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><h3 id="outline__2" class="wp-block-heading">围绕 WACTOR Productions 的问题潜在影响是......</h3><p>但在公司和同一办公室，艺人们陆续不自然地暂停活动，引起部分观众和粉丝的不信任和不满。当人气艺人日南空停止活动时达到顶峰，从 2023 年 2 月左右开始，要求对公司及其办公室的管理立场和人才待遇采取更严格态度的声音浮出水面。截至6月2日，该办公室一直处于混乱状态，所属人才接连休假。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="6iUPNSQxJF"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/wactor-production-should-face-the-voices-of-latin-american-listeners-and-fans-in-response-to-the-successive-suspensions-of-affiliated-vtuber/">WACTOR Productions应该面对的中南美洲观众和粉丝的心声。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“WACTOR Productions 应该面对的中南美洲观众和粉丝的声音继续暂停附属 VTubers 的活动”— P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/wactor-production-should-face-the-voices-of-latin-american-listeners-and-fans-in-response-to-the-successive-suspensions-of-affiliated-vtuber/embed/#?secret=UkOlbBXLR0#?secret=6iUPNSQxJF" data-secret="6iUPNSQxJF" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="47kLvsWOnl"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/former-performer-and-voice-model-for-wactor-production-vtuber-hina-misora-and-tsukito-hana-released-a-statement/">WACTOR Productions VTuber Hinamisora Tsukitohana 前表演者/配音模特发表声明</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“属于 WACTOR Productions 的 VTuber Hinamisora Tsukitohana 的前表演者/声优发表了声明” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/former-performer-and-voice-model-for-wactor-production-vtuber-hina-misora-and-tsukito-hana-released-a-statement/embed/#?secret=RlHxY6OARk#?secret=47kLvsWOnl" data-secret="47kLvsWOnl" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="Xh1PUCNb9E"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/former-performer-and-voice-model-of-vtuber-shino-laila-and-kurari-rose-who-accused-wactor-corporation-releases-latest-statement/">指责WACTOR的前VTuber演员/声优Shinorila Clarirose发表声明</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“指责 WACTOR 的 VTuber Shinolaira Clarirose 的前表演者/配音模特发表声明” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/former-performer-and-voice-model-of-vtuber-shino-laila-and-kurari-rose-who-accused-wactor-corporation-releases-latest-stat